products.name: Iphone 17 Pro
products.description: The iPhone 17 Pro and iPhone 17 Pro Max are available in a new vibrant color called Cosmic Orange, which has been confirmed by multiple sources including Apple's official website and product listings.

products.name: Samsung s25 Ultra
products.description:
The Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra is a high-end smartphone announced on January 22, 2025, and released on February 7, 2025, featuring a 6.9-inch Dynamic LTPO AMOLED 2X display with a QHD+ resolution of 3120 x 1440 pixels, a 120 Hz refresh rate, and a peak brightness of 2600 nits.
 It is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 8 Elite for Galaxy chipset, which includes a 3 nm process, 2x 4.47 GHz Oryon (Phoenix L) and 6x 3.53 GHz Oryon (Phoenix M) CPU cores, and an Adreno 830 GPU.

products.name: MacBook Pro M4
products.description: The latest MacBook Pro with M4 chip delivers exceptional performance for professionals. Featuring a stunning Liquid Retina XDR display, up to 22 hours of battery life, and advanced thermal design for sustained performance.

products.name: Sony WH-1000XM5 Headphones
products.description: Industry-leading noise canceling with Dual Noise Sensor technology. Next-level music with Edge-AI, co-developed with Sony Music Studios Tokyo. Up to 30-hour battery life with quick charge.

products.name: iPad Air M2
products.description: The new iPad Air is supercharged by the M2 chip. With a 10.9-inch Liquid Retina display, Touch ID, and all-day battery life. Perfect for work, creativity, and entertainment.

products.name: Samsung 55" QLED 4K TV
products.description: Experience stunning 4K UHD picture quality with Quantum Dot technology. Smart TV with built-in apps, voice control, and seamless connectivity. Perfect for gaming and streaming.

products.name: AirPods Pro 2nd Gen
products.description: AirPods Pro feature Active Noise Cancellation for immersive sound. Transparency mode for hearing and connecting with the world around you. Up to 30 hours total listening time.

products.name: Classic White Dress Shirt
products.description: Premium cotton dress shirt with a classic fit. Perfect for business meetings, formal events, or everyday professional wear. Features mother-of-pearl buttons and French seams.

products.name: Denim Jacket
products.description: Classic blue denim jacket with a modern slim fit. Made from 100% cotton denim with vintage wash. Perfect for layering or wearing on its own for a casual, stylish look.

products.name: Navy Blue Blazer
products.description: Elegant navy blue blazer crafted from premium wool blend. Features a modern tailored fit, notched lapels, and two-button closure. Versatile piece perfect for business casual or formal occasions.

products.name: Black Leather Jacket
products.description: Premium black leather jacket made from genuine cowhide leather. Features a classic motorcycle style with zipper closure, multiple pockets, and a comfortable fit. Timeless piece for any wardrobe.

products.name: Casual Polo Shirt
products.description: Comfortable polo shirt made from breathable cotton blend. Available in multiple colors with a classic fit. Perfect for casual outings, sports, or weekend wear.

products.name: Dark Wash Jeans
products.description: Premium dark wash jeans with a slim straight fit. Made from 98% cotton and 2% elastane for comfort and stretch. Classic five-pocket design with a mid-rise waist.

products.name: Wool Blend Sweater
products.description: Cozy wool blend sweater perfect for fall and winter. Features a crew neck design, ribbed cuffs and hem, and a comfortable relaxed fit. Available in classic colors.

products.name: Athletic Shorts
products.description: Performance athletic shorts made from moisture-wicking fabric. Features an elastic waistband, side pockets, and a comfortable fit. Perfect for workouts, running, or casual wear.

products.name: Asus ROG Strix G15
products.description:
The ASUS ROG Strix G15 with AMD Ryzen 7, 16GB RAM, 1TB SSD, and NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 graphics is priced at approximately $1,099 on Walmart.com.
 Another variant of the ASUS ROG Strix G15 with a Ryzen 7 6800H processor, 16GB RAM, 1TB SSD, and RTX 3060 graphics is also listed at $1,099 on the same platform.
